About inspiration and where to find it. From blank pages to snow-capped mountains.

More at montblanc.com

Watch the second #MontblancSigned episode on IGTV or go to montblanc.com for more.

node.text:
We celebrated the launch of our latest collaboration by live
streaming with @matveimusic. Watch the full video at montblancxmaisonkitsune.com .

Created in Paris in 2002 by Gildas Loaëc and Masaya Kuroki, Kitsuné offers a unique Art de Vivre blending a fashion brand @maisonkitsune, music label @kitsunemusique and cafés, bars and restaurants @cafekitsune. “Kitsuné”, the Japanese word for “fox”, is a symbol of versatility that according to legend possesses the power to change its appearance. With this new collaboration, their next shape-shifting act is revealed. 
  
Shop the drop montblanc.com

node.text:
Thinking about founding a start-up?
We might have something for you: #RaisingTheStakes, the first episode of our new series #MontblancSigned.
A journey to the early days of a start-up you today might know under the name “Montblanc”.

Watch the first #MontblancSigned episode on IGTV or go to montblanc.com for more.

"Well, I like to write. I don’t type. Pen to paper. The way my brain works, this doesn’t work. It blocks the flow.” — @officialspikelee. Provoking thought since 1986.
Spike Lee leaves his mark not just on the blank page before him, but on all of us. #WhatMovesYouMakesYou

node.text:
@officialspikelee is one of the most original and respected storytellers of our generation. We’re thrilled he’s continuing to working alongside us as one of our Montblanc #MarkMakers.

Director, producer, professor and writer Shelton Jackson “Spike” Lee pushes boundaries and explores challenging themes whenever he puts pen to paper. He embodies our core belief that anyone can leave a mark on the world when they let their passion and intuition guide them. #WhatMovesYouMakesYou

Cillian Murphy's career is one built on following his passions and perfecting his craft. In every role he plays, the audience is aware they are witnessing talent that has been perfected and honed over a lifetime.

Great acting requires elegance, timing and charisma — three qualities that our new Montblanc 1858 Geosphere UltraBlack Limited Edition also happens to have. Tap for more information.

Something which has always moved #CillianMurphy is the electricity of the stage. First as a musician, then as an actor. Always as a performer.

What moves you? #WhatMovesYouMakesYou

Since he first picked up a book, #CillianMurphy understood the power of a great piece of writing ­­– not only to move an audience but to leave them altered. In every new role he takes and every performance he gives, he knows he must do the same.

The power of writing starts by wielding your pen. Here, Murphy wields the StarWalker UltraBlack Fineliner. Tap to shop.

#CillianMurphy’s first experiences on the stage were with a guitar by his side, playing in a rock band alongside his brother. At age 19, he began following another of his passions: acting. Whether playing a survivor of a zombie apocalypse or the swaggering leader of a Birmingham criminal gang, Murphy leaves a mark in the minds of audiences by approaching each new role with audacity and creativity.

We’re proud to welcome him as our Montblanc Mark Maker. #WhatMovesYouMakesYou
